title: Framing Britney Spears
description:
Oops, they did a podcast again! Tig and Cheryl talk the new NY Times Britney Spears doc, "Framing Britney Spears." The discussion somehow leads to Tig and Cheryl sharing some incredible stories about... Barbara Streisand. Plus Cheryl learns to toot her own (clown) horn! *this episode contains spoilers* (tigandcheryltruestory@gmail.com)
